body_html: I am not very familiar with pynq but the only mention of pynq and TF together I could find suggests that pynq is 32-bit. If that's the case I don't think it will work because TensorFlow is 64-bit only.

body: I am not very familiar with pynq but [the only mention of pynq and TF together I could find](https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/pynq_project/kG8ZtRg4k_A) suggests that pynq is 32-bit. If that's the case I don't think it will work because TensorFlow is 64-bit only.
